### Validate Stock Availability
POST http://localhost:8081/api/products/stock/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

